@{b}German name         :@{ub} Wasserstoff
@{b}French name         :@{ub} Hydrogčne

@{b}Symbol              :@{ub} H
@{b}Atomic number       :@{ub} 1
@{b}Isotopes            :@{ub} @{" Overview " link ISOTOP_H}
@{b}State at 25°C       :@{ub} gaseous, non-metal
@{b}Abundance [p.p.m.]  :@{ub} 1520
@{b}Discovered by       :@{ub} Cavendish (1766)

@{b}Elektron configuration :@{ub} 1s^1
@{b}Oxidation states       :@{ub} -1, +1

@{b}Relative atomic mass        :@{ub} 1.0079
@{b}Elektronegativity           :@{ub} 2.20 (Pauling)
@{b}Atomic radius [pm]          :@{ub} 78
@{b}Ionization energie [kJ/mol] :@{ub} 1312.0

@{b}Density [kg/m^3]  :@{ub} 0.08988
@{b}Melting point [K] :@{ub} 14.01
@{b}Boiling point [K] :@{ub} 20.28
