  * = This isotope is not stable and decays.

@next LR
@prev LR
@ENDNODE

@NODE "HELP"  "Hilfe "
@{b}The electron congiguriation of the noble gases in extended form:@{ub}

[He] = 1s^2
[Ne] = 1s^2 2s^2 2p^6
[Ar] = 1s^2 2s^2 2p^6 3s^2 3p^6
[Kr] = 1s^2 2s^2 2p^6 3s^2 3p^6 3d^10 4s^2 4p^6
[Xe] = 1s^2 2s^2 2p^6 3s^2 3p^6 3d^10 4s^2 4p^6 4d^10 5s^2 5p^6
[Rn] = 1s^2 2s^2 2p^6 3s^2 3p^6 3d^10 4s^2 4p^6 4d^10 4f^14 5s^2 5p^6 
       5d^10 6s^2 6p^6

@prev HELP
@next HELP    
@ENDNODE
